Feature: ServerAuthenticationFormWork

  As a user
  I want to save my settings for server authentication from settings form

  Scenario: Restore settings
    Given form settings is not run
    When I run form settings
    Then app restore settings on form: UserName, UserPass

  Scenario: Save settings
    Given notifications settings form is open
    When I press save button
    Then app save settings on form: UserName, UserPass